- All 8 Technical Working Groups linked Key Results Areas became functional. Their respective triennium programme of work as well as budgets were developed and a regular rhythm of planning and decision review meetings was established;

- The general framework for establishing an independent functional Secretariat was developed. These include, a) technical assistance; b)the Guidelines and Standard Operating Procedures; c) Terms and Conditions of Service and; d) interim time-table and budget for instituting the Secretariat

- Support to align sector Institutions’ strategic plans to DGSS resulted in consistent tools for measuring and attributing sector institutions’ contribution to the DGS outcomes
